{"type":"message","id":"6d89bacb","parentId":"341478ca","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:05:49.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经收集了足够的信息。让我进入第三步，整理笔记。我需要把收集到的信息写成笔记保存到 knowledge/ 目录。首先让我检查一下工作目录结构。","thinkingSignature":"ecc1e6a96d4636f1117670af1eb95ea1221a46048b01d408265931349e62bc57"},{"type":"text","text":"## 第二步：阅读提取 (5分钟)\n\n从 Anthropic 工程博客获取到了核心要点：\n\n**核心要点 1：AI Agent 架构模式**\n- Workflows（工作流）：预定义代码路径编排\n- Agents（代理）：LLM 动态自主决策\n- 推荐模式：Prompt Chaining → Routing → Parallelization → Orchestrator-workers → Evaluator-optim\n\n**核心要点 2：三大核心原则**\n- 保持简单性（Simplicity）\n- 透明度（Transparency）：展示 agent 规划步骤\n- ACI（Agent-Computer Interface）：清晰工具文档和测试\n\n**核心要点 3：最佳实践**\n- 优先简单方案，只在需要时增加复杂度\n- Agents = LLM + 工具 + 环境反馈循环\n- 需要沙盒测试和适当 guardrails\n\n---\n\n## 第三步：写作产出 (10分钟)\n\n让我检查 knowledge 目录并写入笔记：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8nylv289g9ve_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la","workdir":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\guan-guan\\workspace"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":12286,"output":278,"cacheRead":36145,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773821135991}}
